					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">XNA did vsync in windowed mode using only calls to present.<br />But if you're really trying to avoid using Direct3D, you could use timers, polling what scanline is currently being displayed, Sleep(1), and timeBeginPeriod.</div>

					
